Version 1.7.2
2023-07-10 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Update some colors to the user interface
* Add hostname to the user interface

Version 1.7.1
2023-07-02 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Fixed deamon/daemon spelling mistakes

Version 1.7.0
2023-07-01 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Changed keybinding CTRL-r to CTRL-l
* Changed keybinding CTRL-a to CTRL-u
* Fixed redrawing the screen
* Added an number of common Unix/Emacs editing keybindings
* Ignored SIGPIPE on close of the client
* Added longopts
* Man pages converted to mdoc format

Version 1.6.3
2021-04-08 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* The drawing loop has been removed and the terminal updated as needed. This removes flickering on slow connections.

Version 1.6.2
2021-05-25 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Fixes a blocking issue when only a single client connects

Version 1.6.1
2021-05-25 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Attempted to fix a blocking issue when only a single client connects

Version 1.6.0
2021-05-25 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Multi-threaded client which removes and reduces polling between the communication socket and keyboard input.
* An internal chat history and basic auto-completion.
* Also many little bug fixes and refinements.

Version 1.5.5
2021-05-25 Ron Wills <ron@digitalcombine.ca>

* Control-R key binding added to redraw the client

